  <summary date="2026-04-15T15:11:53Z" status="Introduced in House">Freedom from Unfair Gun Taxes Act of 2025

This bill prohibits a state&#160;or any political subdivision of a state from imposing or collecting an excise tax on the sale&#160;of a firearm, ammunition, or any part or component of a firearm or ammunition by a manufacture or dealer.&#160;</summary>
